explanation: Sauté, braise, simmer, and poach are all specific cooking methods that involve applying heat to food. Marinating is a cold preparation process to flavor or tenderize food, not a cooking method itself.

Four of the tokens (Colosseum, Petra, Taj Mahal, Great Wall of China) are recognized as part of the 'New7Wonders of the World.' The 'Lighthouse of Alexandria' is one of the 'Seven Wonders of the Ancient World.'
"Ate", "For", "Won", and "To" are homophones for the numbers 'Eight', 'Four', 'One', and 'Two' respectively. 'Blue' does not have a common number homophone.
